---
---

<section id="install" class="install">
  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="head">
      <span class="eyebrow">First launch</span>
      <h2 class="serif">
        Drag, right-click, open. Done in twenty seconds.
      </h2>
      <p class="lede">
        Breaks isn't notarized yet. Apple charges <em>$99 a year</em> for that
        and this is a free side project. macOS will warn you the first time;
        the workaround is small and one-off.
      </p>
    </header>

    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">i.</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="serif">Download the zip.</h3>
          <p>
            From the <a href="https://github.com/GjinPrelvukaj/Breaks/releases/latest" rel="noopener">latest release</a>.
            Universal binary, around one megabyte zipped.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">ii.</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="serif">Move it to <code>/Applications</code>.</h3>
          <p>Same as any other Mac app. Drag and drop.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">iii.</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="serif">Right-click → Open.</h3>
          <p>
            On first launch only. macOS shows a dialog; click <strong>Open</strong>.
            After that it launches normally, forever.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">iv.</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="serif">Or: skip the prompt entirely.</h3>
          <p>One line in Terminal removes the quarantine flag:</p>
<pre><code>xattr -dr com.apple.quarantine /Applications/Breaks.app</code></pre>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .install {
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hair);
  }
  .head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  }
  .head h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.6vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 100, "SOFT" 70;
  }
  .head em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .lede {
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    counter-reset: step;
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
  .steps li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3.2rem 1fr;
    column-gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hair);
  }
  .steps li:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--amber);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
    padding-top: 0.15em;
  }
  .steps h3 {
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 36;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .steps p {
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .steps a {
    color: var(--amber);
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--amber) 40%, transparent);
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .steps a:hover {
    border-color: var(--amber);
  }
  .steps pre {
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
  }
</style>
